This is a working demo of OpenCV Face Recognition based Attendance Management System. You can mark your attendance by just facing the camera.
Technology used:
Python
OpenCV:-  For Image Detection and click Image and save in File
Tkinter:- For Graphical User Interface


Here is youtube link to demonstrate running project.
https://youtu.be/UswiRsn3ZVE

I am improving this project for better performance. Please keep posting your suggestions.
